	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just recently tried playing a bard and was wondering is there a way you can switch from weapons (sword and shield) to instruments in a hurry. Can you make a hot key out of it? If so, how? And is there a better way to juggle songs then playing one right after the other (so that you constantly have the affects of two songs at once) Am I playing this bard right, or am I getting him wrong?<br><br>Shinobi<br>Kane Bayle<br>Lvl 12<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
