<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=103223199739604></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f103223199739604><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=103223199739604>RE: hotkey or something?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=103223199739604#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=135979><span id=Scholar>RavinRed</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>54 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Sep 16th 11:21 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.70]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>All very good advice.&nbsp;&nbsp;See <a href="http://www.eqdiva.com" target=_new>http://www.eqdiva.com</a> for other hints.<br><br>I agree, twist songs OR weapons but both can be tough, especially if you're dual-wielding.  Once you're proficient at a particular instrument skill, most songs can be played without their given instrument, albeit a bit less effective  (WARNING:  There are songs that REQUIRE their instrument, see the website above for more details).  <br><br>My major pain is when I'm hanging back with the casters, just twisting melee buffs or resists with my Lute equiped for Cantana of Soothing during breaks, and suddenly I MUST melee or die.  I jump in and try to beat the mob to death with my treasured Mistmoore Lute while changing to weapons.  The trick:  when holding an instrument, train yourself to ALWAYS grab your secondary slot weapon first, swap out the instrument, then trade the instrument for your primary weapon.  Then at least you're swinging SOMETHING at the mob while you change up.  It may seem obvious to some, but I've wasted precious time trying to do it bass-akwards.<br><br>On the other hand, my Hand-to-Hand skill definately went up :)<br><br>Calthine Faeriesong<br>Bard of the 43rd Song<br>Torture Guild<br>Vazelle<br><br>(who is considering officially changing her name to &quot;Carpal Tunnel&quot;)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
