	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can get the combine instruments from a vendor in Katta Castellum (Maria Whispersong?).&nbsp;&nbsp;The building they are sold in is Starlight Music at approx. loc 550, -250 (marked 1 in the eqatlas map : <a href="http://www.eqatlas.com/luclin/kattacastellummap.html" target=_new>http://www.eqatlas.com/luclin/kattacastellummap.html</a> ). I think it cost me about 140pp to get the drum, lute and horn.<br><br>Getting to Katta Castellum used to be quite scary (at lvl 10) as you had to run through a few 30+  zones to get there, but now with the new wizard and druid port spells, you can get ported into Twilight Sea which is only one zone away.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
